 <br />\n代你發力<br />\n認真的 加油"},{"pid":"08eea0fbc0e2ce6184bd56e9306f3969af3a1682","tid":1468452,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:17:25.000Z","msg":"巴打放心 國難有我地<br />\n好好照顧uncle啦"},{"pid":"4a1922ff6347588c9e80b0ba90ca55c256ac67df","tid":1468452,"uid":190895,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:21:05.000Z","msg":"我爸爸都係因為癌症最近走左 由確診到走都係一年時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕對明你依加感受 <br />\n<br />\n但真心比哂時間去陪佢 雖然呢啲說話好似好行咁  但真係真係珍惜每一日 同埋知道你會好難受 好抑鬱同唔開心。但盡量鼓勵佢多啲 睇下佢有咩心願可以做到就同佢完成下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想傾訴可以上黎呀 大把人陪住你 或者搵我都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我爸爸走左一個月 我都仲好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油呀"},{"pid":"b35763ca1fca8cc06104a77098ec17134b84c167","tid":1468452,"uid":234219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:12.000Z","msg":"巴打 請你好好咁休息 依排你多d去陪下你老豆 佢需要你既陪伴 香港既事 留返俾我地處理<br />\n加油。"},{"pid":"23aca06051452bc467d6203f4f987f81af6beec1","tid":1468452,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:29:26.000Z","msg":"有冇咩先兆徵狀？"},{"pid":"a3c39c6aee5689d0be3dd605216af1690cf371f3","tid":1468452,"uid":134839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:30:08.000Z","msg":"陪下你頭家先啦清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港既家事仲有我地頂住！！"},{"pid":"dd919808372121766ddd588a2b7e9e17ac2c2db9","tid":1468452,"uid":134839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a1922ff6347588c9e80b0ba90ca55c256ac67df","tid":1468452,"uid":190895,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"re